data_case_b_plus_atom
#
# Case B+: Lys78 has TWO independent two-state choices at the SAME residue -- a backbone "loop"
# choice (atoms N,CA,C,O,H) and a side-chain "rotamer" choice (CB,CG,CD,CE,NZ). Both reuse the
# altloc letters A/B on residue 78, so the networks are separated by label_atom_id, not by residue.
#
